node.text:
@goatsneakers: Nike celebrates the 50th anniversary of Carolyn Davidson's Swoosh logo with the Dunk High 'First Use Pack.' A Light Bone leather base with matching suede overlays is paired with Green Noise accents across the Swoosh, laces and heel tab. White text on the quarter panel commemorates the debut of Davidson's iconic design.

Available on the app and GOAT.com

node.text:
Since SS19, Chitose Abe's sacai has worked with Nike, remixing iconic silhouettes with surprising details.

Abe brings her signature approach to 'Classic Green,' reimagining the Blazer Low with two Swooshes, stacked tongues, double lacing and multiple heel counters.

Explore sacai x Nike, only on the app and GOAT.com
